    • Constructor Detail

      • PowerManager

        public PowerManager(float powerCapacity,
                    float inputRate,
                    float outputRate)
        Constructs a new PowerManager.
        Parameters:
        worldObj - The world the manager is in.
        position - The position of the manager.
        powerCapacity - the maximum amount of power the manager can hold.
        inputRate - the maximum amount of power the manager can accept in one tick. Use -1 if the value is infinite.
        outputRate - the maximum amount of power the manager can output in one tick. Use -1 if the value is infinite.
        type - The type of the tile entity (0: generator, 1: wiring, 2: machine, 3: storage)
